# Tutorial: Advanced - Steps 1-4: Release Automation
# Shows: Release workflow commands

Output advanced-01-release.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 15
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

# Title
Type "# Advanced: Release Automation"
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Check release readiness
Type "ait release check"
Enter
Sleep 4s

# Show current status
Type "ait release status"
Enter
Sleep 3s

# Generate release notes
Type "ait release notes"
Enter
Sleep 3s

# Show full workflow (help)
Type "ait release full --help"
Enter
Sleep 3s
